@startmindmap
* Security Testing Scope
** Authentication
*** POST /auth/login
*** Valid and invalid credentials
*** Rate limiting / lockout
*** Expired or tampered token rejected
** Authorization (RBAC)
*** Non-member project access blocked
*** Unauthorized task update blocked
*** Missing Authorization header -> 401
** Input Security
*** SQL injection payload does not bypass
*** XSS payload is output-encoded
** File Security
*** File size limit enforced (>25MB rejected)
*** Type and MIME validation enforced
*** Unauthorized download blocked
*** Path traversal attempt rejected
** Data and Logging
*** Soft-deleted records hidden in normal queries
*** Passwords and tokens are not logged
** Expected HTTP Outcomes
*** 200 / 400 / 401 / 403 / 404 / 413
@endmindmap
